The paper deals with relay selection and link adaptation in wireless networks, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The use of distributed beamforming and the proposed signaling mechanism also suggest that the paper could fall under the systems and control (cs.SY) category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of modulation and coding schemes (MCS), which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography (cs.CR).
